{"tid":1293794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港市民一齊控告警察，利用法庭迫使引入第三方調查","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T09:51:18.000Z","uid":258597,"like":85,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e57831612ca6dbb2a8b8b93db4a841991ec190d2","tid":1293794,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"大家，監警會係７月２日成立調查舉行傳媒簡布會。話要調查呢１２１個投訴個案，至於成效係點（0.09％）。成功左又會點？相信唔洗我多講大家都明。所以，我好希望全香港既市民，一齊集資控告警務處處長，利用僅餘既法庭力量調查警方有冇係呢一個月既時間中有冇濫權。我無讀法律，唔太清楚司法程序既詳情，或者真係開庭告警務處處長既時候由邊方調查。希望各位巴絲比下意見。其實係２０１６年旺角事件，都有明報記者去入稟索償。大家可以參考下。<br />\n<br />\n引入法庭審訊，還警察公道。無事唔洗怕比人查。<br />\n<br />\n採訪旺角騷亂疑遭警襲擊 記者入稟索償（ＮＯＷＴＶ）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=336456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336456&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=d8c0d00e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336456&h=60c4f628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=336456</a><br />\n<br />\n監警會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/home/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhome%2Findex.html&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=37f1d6cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/home/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n東網（投訴成功率20190605）有幾高就自己睇啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190605/bkn-20190605092709123-0605_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190605%2Fbkn-20190605092709123-0605_00822_001.html&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=55c5c474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190605/bkn-20190605092709123-0605_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d5173d0e65ef29a60ad8e2a00e3f223431eede78","tid":1293794,"uid":107686,